# NFC personalization subproject (scripts/nfc-personalization/)
# Already covered by global .env and node_modules/ rules above, listed
# explicitly here because the .env contains the most sensitive secrets
# of the entire project (NTAG424_K_PICC and NTAG424_MASTER_KEY).
# DO NOT REMOVE these lines without thinking very hard.
scripts/**/node_modules/
scripts/**/.env
scripts/**/*.log